                                        <span class="font-body-md text-body-md font-semibold text-on-surface">Kapadokya Balon Turu</span>
                                    </div>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Macera</td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md font-medium">154</td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md font-bold text-primary">₺616,000</td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4">
                                    <span class="text-success flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-bold">
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">trending_up</span> 18%
                                    </span>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4">
                                    <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold">Aktif</span>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr class="hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-colors group">
                                <td class="px-6 py-4">
                                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                        <img class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg object-cover" data-alt="A high-contrast wide shot of the Hagia Sophia grand dome against a clear blue sky in Istanbul. The architecture is detailed and majestic, emphasizing historical significance and cultural depth. The lighting is sharp and natural, creating a bright and clean professional atmosphere." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAW_qR9Y12p4QPgm9H1WuMLG3Vy0rUiBBMW8XlDKOcztMKZW2jjcBsKuvwx3JmAIgO4mYvVi3X2cKx1BfoC1e8hNtC02BUwYxFDtFbtCG-R1scRgPL6ip8owrDZuAx8kAQGEJokEXURruclYe8kl6r5IvRz99q_-ISz_GlU1hgZA8OEq7qnlvPYRqKKnvca6nZ-k5HygFsHq5BVJhuIZVXQk8HTbdUnmoe5REaKSmurQn2ZZCAB_MQi6AFUsm02TwmVrA89c4N6nWw" />
                                        <span class="font-body-md text-body-md font-semibold text-on-surface">İstanbul Kültür Mirası</span>
                                    </div>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Kültür</td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md font-medium">210</td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md font-bold text-primary">₺315,000</td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4">
                                    <span class="text-success flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-bold">
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">trending_up</span> 5%
                                    </span>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4">
                                    <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold">Aktif</span>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr class="hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-colors group">
                                <td class="px-6 py-4">
                                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                        <img class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg object-cover" data-alt="A vibrant and appetizing close-up of traditional Turkish Mezes served in a modern, upscale restaurant in Santorini. The colors are rich with greens, reds, and creamy whites. The shallow depth of field keeps the focus on the fresh ingredients, conveying a premium culinary experience. Bright, airy Mediterranean lighting." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAeJzZXNrqCFOQFhlQ5Fx_d82d1lROHdKZlAwW-rhD5WTSpRxsfTxmmnnOjvAmYkb43Eo62cZ2aPBi6JA9vBkzAkwklC-W_6sISc90gV8KQCFGfv8oBI1pNH5ygBecpXnef-4o0LBHZjaTh08wx7gcTznO01vK5Gpy9iYOHZbLExGlz0vxy53hG6Z1IgZ85CaCLxrEabGGx-ofdqDFrn-2YRC42RXVgTbOYYMJUTS7fcMPkcNtc5HAlIlmw1pbRVcfwc35bgeupKcs" />
                                        <span class="font-body-md text-body-md font-semibold text-on-surface">Ege Gastronomi Yolu</span>
                                    </div>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Gastronomi</td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md font-medium">92</td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md font-bold text-primary">₺184,000</td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4">
                                    <span class="text-error flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-bold">
                                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">trending_down</span> 3%
                                    </span>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-6 py-4">
                                    <span class="bg-orange-100 text-orange-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold">Kontenjan Az</span>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr class="hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-colors group">
                                <td class="px-6 py-4">
                                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                        <img class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg object-cover" data-alt="A luxury yacht interior looking out towards the turquoise waters of the Mediterranean coast. The style is minimalist and elegant with neutral wood tones and clean white textiles. The mood is serene, exclusive, and high-end corporate leisure. The lighting is bright and summery." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAKz9lnJlRGqhRsQoCD8y5EVpn3R5Yjoml2aRO19i2DbZ1ihLT5wJ02nKkdNStyqOchO3mcLGR5Yp1K3YhwAaemMxaW7HjvFe7VMcU46jENcBpjafvAI14MNbJQf5A0qKGDA_5UpgCvlmS_MYyKf3rwjrE0Hka1yIRbCV_cj_zprJCS2qm95jyQYhIppNJSYFmwd_NHffn94i52cGhYUB_bc3d9pFS1KX6Y5nOdIFgEVc5Tgh5dnHo00tk_NDP5GGxuU85vzqyEoj4" />
